. ops
.. init
tapelist is created by amlabel, use /etc/amanda/tapelist.tmpl to seed
 amtape full inventory
 amlabel full full-108 slot 20
set tape to start with:
 amtape full inventory
 amtape full slot 12
protect used tapes
 amtape full inventory
 for i in {07..10}; do amadmin full no-reuse full-3$i; done

.. client setup
 sudo 
 echo "# amanda client
service amanda
{
        socket_type             = stream
        protocol                = tcp
        wait                    = no
